name: Sun Company Outsider Zipper Pull with 4 Outdoor Essential Tools
categories: Outsider Zipper Pull with 4 Outdoor Essential
description: Bump up the feature set of your zipper-pull with the Outsider 4-in-1 survival multitool.Thermometer reads in Fahrenheit and Celsius scales down to -20º F and -30º C.Compact, glowing compass – metal parts can be detached for more accurate compass readings.Fire steel and striker are safely tucked away until you need them.Whistle for signalling.Compact design can be a keyring or a zipper-pull.
